message: Hi Bob, I'm excited to offer you this incredible product that I think you'll love. I'm willing to let it go for $12000. What do you think?
I appreciate your enthusiasm, Alice, but I was thinking more along the lines of $9000. I really like the product, but I'm on a tight budget. Can you meet me in the middle?
I understand you're on a tight budget, Bob, but I have to make a profit on this sale. I'm willing to meet you halfway, but I need to get at least $11000 for the product. Can you consider that?
I appreciate your willingness to meet me halfway, Alice, but I'm still a bit short on budget. I'd be willing to go up to $10000 for the product. Can you consider that?
